A project for analyzing the housing market using hadoop, HBase, Mahout, and similar cloud technologies.

This is designed to run using CDH 4.5.0.  It is being developed on the cloudera 4.5.0 virtual machine.

It's not tested on other systems.

The project uses data downloaded from Zillow.  The data is saved in HBase.  In time, the project will
do several intelligent algorithms on the data such as clustering, classification, etc.

The long term goal is to find the best investment opportunities in the market.
